=> highlevel, object oriented programming lang
=> Developed by Sun Microsystems in 1995
=> used for desktop, web, andriod, enterprise system
=>

* OOPS => Java supports OOPs concepts create modular and reusable code
* Platform Independence => java programs can run on any OS with JVM
* Robust and secure => reliability, security memory management and exception handling
* Multithreading and concurrency => executes multiple tasks for efficiency
* Rich API And Standard Libraries => buildin libraries
* Frameworks for web dev
* Open source libraries
* Maintainability and Scalability



What we can do with java???

1. Mobile App = Android studio
2. Web Dev = Spring, Spring Boot, Structs, Hibernate
3. Desktop GUI App = Libraris like JavaFX, Swing
4. Enterprise application = Backbone for banking, ERP, Largescale business software
5. Game Dev = LibGDX, jMonkeyengine
6. Big Data Tech = Hadoop , Apache Kafka
7. IOT =
8. Cloud-based app  => AWS, Azure and google cloud
